Package: fcscrapR
Type: Package
Title: Compiling soccer commentary data from ESPN for easy use in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ron", "Yurko", role = c("aut", "cre"),email = "ryurko21@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Ron Yurko <ryurko21@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows data driven sports enthusiasts to easily access
    event data for soccer games from ESPN. The functions within this package help
    find, parse, and clean the commentary data from ESPN for R users.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0),
         magrittr
Imports: RCurl,
         stringr,
         lubridate,
         dplyr,
         zoo,
         scrapeR,
         rvest,
         xml2,
         purrr
Suggests: testthat,
          knitr,
          rmarkdown
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/ryurko/fcscrapR
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
